  "slug": "vegetarian-sausage-roll",
  "title": "Vegetarian Sausage Roll",
  "subtitle": "Puff pastry filled with a mushroom, lentil, and cheese mixture that bakes to a satisfying bite",
  "excerpt": "A vegetarian sausage roll needs a filling with enough fat and texture to stand in for the pork. Chestnut mushrooms, green lentils, cheddar, and herbs give a filling that has both substance and flavour, and holds together when sliced or bitten.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "British vegetarian adaptation of the traditional pork sausage roll. Yotam Ottolenghi, Plenty (2010): mushroom-based savoury filling techniques. Contemporary British vegetarian baking practice.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The problem with most vegetarian sausage rolls is water. Mushrooms are 90% water; if you do not cook that water out before rolling them in pastry, the moisture will leak into the puff pastry and prevent it from rising. The solution is a ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "duxelles",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp5nj45x0000z0v4m10lue9v"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " method: cook the mushrooms over high heat until the pan is dry and the mushrooms have reduced to a concentrated, dark paste.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The lentils provide protein and bind the filling. The cheddar melts slightly and holds the roll together once it sets. An ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "egg wash",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr4fow0000qov42zdzjg6a"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " is what makes the difference between a pale roll and a golden one.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
